name: Tani Adult Version
description:
Tani x Little Monster x Thai ghost

This is my collaboration project with Ayeer.Studio. I've changed her little monster character that cosplay to Tani (A Thai traditional ghost which appears as a young woman that haunts wild banana trees known generically as lady of the wood.) to an abstract art. The concept is talking about the little monster that want to explore the world. I design it into strong version to represent concept of monster. It likes an adult version of Tani.
